{"tid":1077420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙特姊妹獲簽證往安全第三國　上周已離港　促勿低估勇敢女子力量","createTime":"2019-03-25T14:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T02:17:47.000Z","uid":20058,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8d3be4b5e183d0d9b1faba004012c43ca363c637","tid":1077420,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T14:40:35.000Z","msg":"消息透過韋智達律師行facebook公布，20歲的Reem與18歲的Rawan表示，希望她們的經歷可以為面對類似情況的人帶來希望，又稱要大聲、清楚地向沙特阿拉伯當局和其他「不平等對待女性」的政權說：「永遠不要低估勇敢女子的力量。」<br />\n<br />\n韋智達在聲明指出，Reem和Rawan已在第三國，作為自由的年輕女子過新生活，努力融入當地文化，並為新家園貢獻。兩姊妹並希望感謝本地和國際傳媒，以及過去半年曾無私地幫助她們的人。韋智達表示，為確保Reem和Rawan日後安全，故不會公布兩人身在哪個國家，她們亦不會再接受訪問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190325/s00001/1553518202394/%e6%b2%99%e7%89%b9%e5%a7%8a%e5%a6%b9%e7%8d%b2%e7%b0%bd%e8%ad%89%e5%be%80%e5%ae%89%e5%85%a8%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%89%e5%9c%8b-%e4%b8%8a%e5%91%a8%e5%b7%b2%e9%9b%a2%e6%b8%af-%e4%bf%83%e5%8b%bf%e4%bd%8e%e4%bc%b0%e5%8b%87%e6%95%a2%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%90%e5%8a%9b%e9%87%8f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190325%2Fs00001%2F1553518202394%2F%25e6%25b2%2599%25e7%2589%25b9%25e5%25a7%258a%25e5%25a6%25b9%25e7%258d%25b2%25e7%25b0%25bd%25e8%25ad%2589%25e5%25be%2580%25e5%25ae%2589%25e5%2585%25a8%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25b8%2589%25e5%259c%258b-%25e4%25b8%258a%25e5%2591%25a8%25e5%25b7%25b2%25e9%259b%25a2%25e6%25b8%25af-%25e4%25bf%2583%25e5%258b%25bf%25e4%25bd%258e%25e4%25bc%25b0%25e5%258b%2587%25e6%2595%25a2%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%25ad%2590%25e5%258a%259b%25e9%2587%258f&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbqwy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=fdc1586f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190325%2Fs00001%2F1553518202394%2F%25e6%25b2%2599%25e7%2589%25b9%25e5%25a7%258a%25e5%25a6%25b9%25e7%258d%25b2%25e7%25b0%25bd%25e8%25ad%2589%25e5%25be%2580%25e5%25ae%2589%25e5%2585%25a8%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25b8%2589%25